Class FastLookupToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.util.FastLookupToken

  • @Immutable
public final class FastLookupToken
extends Object
    Container class that holds a text span, actual text, and possible variant text for a lookup token. This class maintains (forces) lowercase text for lookup Author: SPF Affiliation: CHIP-NLP Date: 11/29/13
